.* 04/12/06 RPI244 IGNORE DSORG=                  
.* 06/14/07 RPI 641 DEFAULT MF=I
.* 08/21/07 RPI 670 CORRECT REG OPTIMIZATION TO HANDLE ANY REG SYMBOL
.* 04/19/06 RPI 833 add SETC quotes for HLASM compatibility       
